name: "Every day" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
Yes, I am living because I can't die and I don't know what to do.
 
I have so much disillusionment and at the same time so much loneliness, that it weighs like a 100 kilos backpack. 
I don't feel like opening my eyes every day and start breathing.
I feel anxious as time goes on, more and more every day. 
 
I feel like I'm hurting myself and I don't want to go through with it, but something deep down inside pushes me to keep going.

Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art.
With different editing tools.
